{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, a grey literature search was conducted on Google Scholar in order to identify and include studies published between June 2022 and June 2023.",
    "Box 1 presents the unique search keywords used to search the databases.",
    "The exact search strategy and the keywords associated with the search in all the databases are available in Supplementary Table 1.",
    "The search results were exported as multiple XML files, merged, imported into the Covidence web application for systematic review 54, and duplicates were removed.",
    "The reference lists of included studies were searched to identify any additional relevant studies."
  ]
}